# Revision 1.4  1994/02/03  23:53:00  decipher
# Updated to allow setting the "DECIPHER" environment externally, or else to default
# to the latest frozen version of the system.
#
# Revision 1.3  1993/09/27  09:04:28  decipher
# Updated to use the official location for the DECIPHER System.
